sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller as Shared caller
    participant Factory as CreateOpcUaServices
    participant Session as OpcUaSession
    participant Channel as UA channel/session
    participant Sub as OpcUaSubscription
    participant Peer as Remote OPC UA server

    Caller->>Factory: create data services
    Factory->>Session: construct OpcUaSession
    Factory-->>Caller: DataServices bundle

    Caller->>Session: Connect(params)
    Session->>Channel: Connect
    Channel->>Peer: open channel
    Peer-->>Channel: connected
    Session->>Channel: CreateSession + ActivateSession
    Channel->>Peer: session handshake
    Peer-->>Channel: activated
    Session-->>Caller: connect resolved

    Caller->>Session: Read / Write / Browse / Call
    Session->>Channel: service request
    Channel->>Peer: UA service call
    Peer-->>Channel: service result
    Channel-->>Session: OPC UA result
    Session-->>Caller: SCADA-native result

    Caller->>Session: CreateMonitoredItem
    Session->>Sub: lazy-create default subscription
    Sub->>Channel: CreateSubscription / CreateMonitoredItems
    Channel->>Peer: subscription requests
    Peer-->>Channel: notifications
    Channel-->>Sub: data changes / events
    Sub-->>Caller: monitored-item handlers
